summary:
Here is a family tree featuring Haida, Retsuko and the family members that was made by @kingdomofkitten
First generation is...
body:
Here is a family tree featuring Haida, Retsuko and the family members that was made by @kingdomofkitten

First generation is Ryoko, Retsuko’s paternal grandmother.

Second generation is Hisoka and Harumi, Haida’s Parents. Along with Ryoto and Rie, Retsuko’s Parents.

Third generation is Haida and his older sister Hiroko. As well as Retsuko and her younger siblings, Riko and her twin Ryuu.

Fourth generation is Haida and Retsuko’s son Ikari. It’s also funny how he’s the odd name out on both sides of his family, since everybody on dad’s side starts with ‘H’ and his mom’s side starts with ‘R’ and he starts with ‘I.’

Might color someday, but no promises…
